      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a permanent resident of Kerala.\n1. The applicant should be a student.\n1. The applicant should be studying in Government / Aided Institution in Kerala.\n1. The financial assistance will be given to the students who are studying in Class 9th to Post-Graduation.\n1. The applicant who has 40% or more disability is eligible to apply under the scheme.\n1. The applicant’s annual family income is not applicable under this scheme.\n\n**Note:** The preference will be given to the students of Below Poverty Line (BPL) category.\n",
